This paper deals with natural language processing and neural networks, which are typically covered in the Computer Science sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). The use of attention-based methods and transfer learning also suggests that this paper could fall under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
